text: Gad Elmaleh ( Gād el-Māleḥ; born 19 April 1971) is a Moroccan-Canadian stand- up comedian and actor. He is known as the "Seinfeld of France". His best known movie roles were in Coco, Priceless, La Doublure and Midnight in Paris. ==References== Category:1971 births Category:Living people Category:Canadian movie actors Category:Canadian television actors Category:Canadian voice actors Category:Canadian comedians Category:People from Casablanca Category:Naturalized citizens of Canada
